      <h2 class="h2">Wherever I lay my hat...</h2>
      <div class="row  no-gutters ">
        <p class="col-lg-8 col-12 intro">The nature of digital working – especially now – is that we should be able to deliver fantastic work from anywhere. And we do. That said, we also love collaborating face-to-face (and lunch-to-lunch) with our colleagues and clients, too. As such, we have four Digital office ‘hubs’, with client onsite working and remote working alongside that. Some of our colleagues are also based out of other lovely PA offices, too, spreading the Digital love.</p>
      </div>
