          <p class="horizontal-card__text">Possibly the PA office with the most post-it notes, Farringdon is home to around 70 of our digital designers, engineers, strategists and anyone who likes to be near a well-stocked biscuit tin. There are lots of sofas, a good few project rooms and plenty of windows, encouraging collaborative, positive vibes. We’re a short hop from our friends in the Victoria office and some of the best food and drink in London.</p>
